{"kanda":6,"sarga":33,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"सीतांतुमोहितांदृष्टवासरमानामराक्षसी ।आससादाथवैदेहींप्रियांप्रणयिनींसखी","trans":"Then seeing Sita in distraught, a Rakshasi by name Saarana who was very dear and friendly with Vaidehi approached her.","words":[{"d":"अथ","m":"then"},{"d":"प्रणयिनीम्","m":"dear"},{"d":"सखी","m":"friend"},{"d":"सरमानाम","m":"Saarana"},{"d":"राक्षसी","m":"rakshasa मोहिताम् distraught"},{"d":"सीताम्","m":"Sita"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"प्रियाम्","m":"friend"},{"d":"वैदेहीम्","m":"Vaidehi"},{"d":"आससाद","m":"approached"}]},{"v":2,"dev":"मोहितांराक्षसेन्द्रेणसीतांपरमदुःखिताम् ।आश्वासयामासतदासरमामृदुभाषिणी","trans":"Then Saarana of sweet expression, comforted Sita who was put off and was extremely sorrowful because of the Rakshasa king.","words":[{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"मृदुभाषिणी","m":"of sweet expression"},{"d":"सरमा","m":"Saarana"},{"d":"राक्षसेन्द्रेण","m":"because of the king of Rakshasa"},{"d":"मोहिताम्","m":"put off"},{"d":"परमदुःखिताम्","m":"extremely sorrowful"},{"d":"सीताम्","m":"Sita"},{"d":"आश्वासयामास","m":"comforted."}]},{"v":3,"dev":"साहितत्रकृतामित्रंसीतयारक्ष्यमाणया ।रक्षन्तीरावणादिष्टासानुक्रोशादृढव्रता","trans":"Most compassionate Saarana, determined to protect was friendly with Sita while she was ordered for protecting her by Ravana.","words":[{"d":"रावणादिष्टा","m":"by Ravana's order"},{"d":"रक्षन्ती","m":"protected"},{"d":"सानुक्रोशा","m":"most compassionate"},{"d":"दृढव्रता","m":"determined"},{"d":"सा","m":"that"},{"d":"तत्र","m":"there"},{"d":"रक्ष्यमाणया","m":"protecting"},{"d":"सीतया","m":"Sita"},{"d":"मित्रम्","m":"friendship"},{"d":"कृताहि","m":"was doing (protecting)."}]},{"v":4,"dev":"साददर्शसखीसीतांसरमानष्टचेतनाम् ।उपावृत्त्योत्थितांध्वस्तांबडबामिवपांसुलाम्","trans":"Saarana saw her friend Sita, who had lost consciousness, fully covered by dust by rolling on the dirty ground like a female horse.","words":[{"d":"सखी","m":"friend"},{"d":"सा","m":"that"},{"d":"सरमा","m":"Saarana"},{"d"